@alanbuchanan branches are not really deleted until `git clean` is run (*which happens once a month* IIRC)
So basically, your feature branch is hanging somewhere.
Check the reflog `git reflog` to know the commit sha of the feature branch and `git checkout -b feature-branch <commit-hash>`

